  "prompt": "What does \"AAA\" mean in AAA title game?",
  "response": "In the context of video games, \"AAA\" refers to games that are developed and published by major companies with substantial budgets for both development and marketing. These games are often characterized by their high production values, advanced technology, and widespread promotional efforts. The term \"AAA\" is similar to other industries' use of the term to denote top-tier quality or elite status, indicating that these games are expected to perform well in terms of sales and critical reception.",
